metadata.name: Ascent
metadata.description:
Ascent  
#001 

Ascent is the first of this collection which observes a trapped, lost soul overcoming the darkness and ascending to the heavens above.

Elsewhen Pathos is a multi-medium, audio-visual collection that explores different points in time across various, unique ethereal planes, seeking to invoke a pathos connection.

Main Website:  
elsewhenpathos.xyz
